reviewText: I just love and respect Venus Williams and for me she is the Best. Such Class and Grace and Strength in all ways
Very informative. I always thought Billie Jean King acted alone in securing equal pay for the Slams.

Excellent film about equal pay for women and the central role that Venus Williams played in achieving that in tennis. Plus it has the added bonus of lots of great tennis footage and interviews with Venus Williams, Billie Jean King and others.  Bravo and thank you to Ms. Williams & the filmmakers.
